<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Processes other than fire primarily disturb stands, including landslides, slope creep, flooding, and tidal influence. The willow sprouts after disturbance, including fire.</div>
